Spring Cloud Stream:

    整合stream：
        1.加依赖
            <dependency>
                <groupId>com.alibaba.cloud</groupId>
                <artifactId>spring-cloud-starter-stream-rocketmq</artifactId>
            </dependency>
        2.加注解
            启动类加上 @EnableBinding(Source.class)
        3.加配置
            Spring:
                cloud:
                    stream:
                          rocketmq:
                            binder:
                              name-server: 127.0.0.1:9876
                          bindings:
                            output:
                              # 用来指定topic
                              destination: stream-test-topic